#parse('includes/head.vm')
#navTabs('Details')

<div class="container-fluid">
		    		
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
		<h4>$member.firstName $member.lastName - Reset password</h4>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr/>
	
	<p>Reseting this member's password will erase their current password and assign them a new one.</p>

	<p>You would normally only want todo this if the user has forgotten their password and has not been able to reset it themselves using the forgotten password option on the signin screen.</p>
	
	<p>After you press the Reset password button the user's new access details will be displayed on your screen.
	You will be given the option of having these details automatically mailed to the user.</p>

	<p>If this member has been are having problems receiving automatic mails from the system you should manually forward these details to the member from your own email address.</p>
		
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
	
			<form>
				<div class="control-group">			
					<div class="controls">
						<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Update details</button>
						#cancel($urlBuilder.memberUrl($member.id))			
					</div>
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
		    	    				
</div>
<hr/>

